{
  "info": {
    "name": "Liverpool Users API",
    "_postman_id": "liverpool-users-api-v1",
    "description": "Microservicio de gestión de usuarios con integración COPOMEX.\n\nBase URL: {{baseUrl}}\n\nEstructura:\n- POST   /api/v1/users        → Crear usuario\n- GET    /api/v1/users        → Listar usuarios (paginado)\n- GET    /api/v1/users/:id    → Obtener usuario por ID\n- PATCH  /api/v1/users/:id    → Actualización parcial\n- DELETE /api/v1/users/:id    → Eliminar usuario\n\nVariable de entorno requerida: {{baseUrl}} = http://localhost:8080",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8080",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string",
      "description": "Se actualiza automáticamente al crear un usuario"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Crear usuario",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Crear usuario — Exitoso (201)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 201 Created', () => {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Respuesta tiene id', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json).to.have.property('id');",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('userId', json.id);",
                  "    console.log('userId guardado:', json.id);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Dirección enriquecida por COPOMEX', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.expect(json.address).to.have.property('municipality');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.address).to.have.property('state');",
                  "    pm.expect(json.address.neighborhoods).to.be.an('array');",
                  "});"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ana\",\n  \"paternalLastName\": \"López\",\n  \"maternalLastName\": \"Martínez\",\n  \"email\": \"ana.lopez@example.com\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"06600\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v1", "users"]
            },
            "description": "Crea un nuevo usuario. El código postal se envía a COPOMEX para resolver la dirección completa automáticamente.\n\n**Validaciones:**\n- name: obligatorio\n- paternalLastName: obligatorio\n- email: obligatorio, formato válido\n- postalCode: obligatorio, exactamente 5 dígitos"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 Created — Usuario creado",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Ana\",\n  \"paternalLastName\": \"López\",\n  \"maternalLastName\": \"Martínez\",\n  \"email\": \"ana.lopez@example.com\",\n  \"postalCode\": \"06600\"\n}"
                },
                "url": {"raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/users", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v1", "users"]}
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": \"64a1b2c3d4e5f6a7b8c9d0e1\",\n  \"name\": \"Ana\",\n  \"paternalLastName\": \"López\",\n  \"maternalLastName\": \"Martínez\",\n  \"email\": \"ana.lopez@example.com\",\n  \"address\": {\n    \"postalCode\": \"06600\",\n    \"municipality\": \"Cuauhtémoc\",\n    \"state\": \"Ciudad de México\",\n    \"city\": \"Ciudad de México\",\n    \"neighborhoods\": [\"Juárez\", \"Cuauhtémoc\", \"Roma Norte\"],\n    \"country\": \"México\"\n  }\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Crear usuario — Error 400 (validación)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Status 400 Bad Request', () => {",
                  "    pm.response.to.have.status(400);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "pm.test('Respuesta tiene estructura de error', () => {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
